        "TileImage": "$($repository bebd3f71-99e4-40e3-b71a-80f3279e2b0e).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, agent. This contract comes with a couple stipulations.\r\rThe first and most important is this - you MUST use the Custom 5mm pistol, and nothing else! The pistol is the only item in your loadout. This gun only can shoot five times.\r\rAdditionally, because of some silly roodypoo, when I killed the church jabronie with the bell, it did not count as falling object, however you MUST use the falling bell to eliminate Arnaldo.\r\rSpare your bullets where you can, and best of luck, 47.",
